Nagios for wth monitoring

Steps to activate nagios monitoring include

(1) install nagios

(2) configure and copy check plugin check_wth to /usr/lib/nagios/plugins/check_wth

(3) configure and copy weatherstation.cfg to /etc/nagios/objects

(4) edit /etc/nagios/nagios.cfg and add the follwong two lines which 
    represent weatherstation definitions
--
# Definitions for monitoring weatherstation
cfg_file=/etc/nagios/objects/weatherstation.cfg
--

